title: Ep 325 | Missy Makes Jase Squirm AGAIN & No One Likes the Name Jase Wants His Grandkids to Call Him
description:
Missy’s presence makes Jase extremely nervous, and it never gets old for Al. Jase explains why he was the preaching student with the most visits to the dean's office. Missy is the worst gold digger ever. Lisa confesses she didn't feel worthy of being a preacher's wife and teases her upcoming book with Miss Kay. Missy does her best Phil impression. And Al can't stop laughing at the odd name Jase wants his grandchildren to call him.
